<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFE26A5DFD2895531B03B848" pageId="25" pageNumber="783" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFE26A5DFD2895531B03B848" blockId="25.[723,1315,668,1087]" pageId="25" pageNumber="783">
Specimens attributed to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFE26A5DFBD595531A93B819" box="[1065,1171,778,811]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Pipustrellus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="25" pageNumber="783" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="wattsi">P. wattsi</taxonomicName>
were originally included under 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFE26A5DFBED956B1A80B861" baseAuthorityName="Temminck" baseAuthorityYear="1840" box="[1041,1152,818,851]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="783" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tenuis">P. tenuis</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFE26A5DFB36956B1D26B848" baseAuthorityName="Peters &amp; Doria" baseAuthorityYear="1881" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="783" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="papuanus">P. papuanus</taxonomicName>
until it was described. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFE26A5DFD2F95D91D5DB8FB" pageId="25" pageNumber="783" type="distribution">
<caption id="90EB6676FFE26A5DFD2F95D91D5DB8FB" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6397868" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6397868" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6397868/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="783" targetBox="[107,699,670,1084]" targetPageId="25">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFE26A5DFD2F95D91D5DB8FB" blockId="25.[723,1315,668,1087]" pageId="25" pageNumber="783">
